OL,6,FPolice say they have been unable to
OL,7,Fidentify any of the human ashes
OL,8,Frecovered from a funeral firm at the
OL,9,Fcentre of a major investigation.
OL,11,FThe ashes, along with 35 bodies, were
OL,12,Fremoved from Legacy Independent
OL,13,FFuneral Directors in Hull last month
OL,14,Fafter police received a report of
OL,15,Fconcern about the "care of the
OL,16,Fdeceased".
OL,18,FTwo people have been arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of fraud and preventing a
OL,20,Flawful burial.
