OL,6,FHumberside Police said they believed
OL,7,Fthey knew the identities of all those
OL,8,Fwhose bodies had been moved, but
OL,9,Fformal identification was still taking
OL,10,Fplace.
OL,12,FIn an update on Thursday 4 April,
OL,13,Fofficers said the ashes were
OL,14,Funidentifiable.
OL,16,FAssistant Chief Constable Thom
OL,17,FMcLoughlin said: "We have been working
OL,18,Fclosely with forensic scientists and
OL,19,Fspecialists to assess whether it was
OL,20,Fpossible to extract DNA from the human
OL,21,Fashes in order to identify them.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/10
