OL,6,F"This will, of course, be devastating
OL,7,Fnews for families and loved ones and
OL,8,Fyou have my heartfelt condolences at
OL,9,Fthis difficult time."
OL,11,F'Fraudulent activity'
OL,13,FThe force launched its investigation
OL,14,Fon 6 March after concerns were raised
OL,15,Fabout "care for the deceased".
OL,17,FA team of 120 police officers and
OL,18,Fcivilian staff has been working on the
OL,19,Finvestigation and a dedicated phone
OL,20,Fline was set up for people with
OL,21,Fconcerns.
