OL,6,FOn Thursday the force said it had
OL,7,Freceived more than 2,000 calls.
OL,9,FMr McLoughlin said a "significant
OL,10,Fnumber" were concerned about the
OL,11,Fidentification of ashes.
OL,13,F"This weekend officers from the
OL,14,Finvestigation team have been in
OL,15,Fcontact with over 700 families to
OL,16,Fupdate them regarding the scientific
OL,17,Fadvice and offer support," he said.
