OL,6,FIn the last three weeks, Hull City
OL,7,FCouncil said checks had been carried
OL,8,Fout at 50 funeral directors in the
OL,9,Fwake of the investigation into Legacy.
OL,11,FThe local authority say it was "very
OL,12,Fclear" the investigation was "in no
OL,13,Fway typical".
OL,15,FSpeaking on Thursday, director of
OL,16,Fpublic protection Angela Dearing said:
OL,17,F"While the sector is not formally
OL,18,Fregulated nationally, the visits were
OL,19,Fan opportunity for us to look at a
OL,20,Fnumber of key areas of funeral
OL,21,Fdirectors' business.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/10
