OL,6,F"These voluntary visits were conducted
OL,7,Fin partnership with funeral directors,
OL,8,Fin order to give reassurances to
OL,9,Fcustomers and our local funeral
OL,10,Fdirectors.
OL,12,F"All the businesses we visited were
OL,13,Freceptive if any advice or suggestions
OL,14,Fwere made."
OL,16,FSupport for affected families
OL,18,FThe council said affected families
OL,19,Fwould not have to pay for new funerals
OL,20,Ffor their loved ones.
