OL,6,FA helpline remains open for practical
OL,7,Fand emotional support.
OL,9,FIn a message to the public, director
OL,10,Fof public health Julia Weldon said:
OL,11,F"We recognise that this has been an
OL,12,Fexceptionally difficult time for
OL,13,Ffamilies and our community, my heart
OL,14,Fgoes out to you all.
OL,16,F"I wanted to let you know we are here
OL,17,Ffor all those affected directly or
OL,18,Findirectly across our community.
